@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_oyctrh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = 0.63
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v1 + 0.06) * (v2 + 0.30 / v2 + 1.00)))
    v0 = wp.cos(v0)
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.cos(v1 + 0.91)))
    v0 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.15 + v0 + 0.19)) * ((v1 + 0.88 + v2 + 0.02) / (tmp + 0.98 - v2 + 0.50)))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin((tmp + 0.55 * tmp + 0.88)))
    v1 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v2 + 0.30) + (v0 + 0.04 * v2 + 0.22)))
    data[tid] = v0
